==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Jim-crow
<hw>Jim"-crow`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>For negroes only;
set aside for used of negroes as a policy of racial
discrimination.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Jim-crow</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Jim-crow
<hw>Jim"-crow`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Mach.)</fld>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>A machine for bending or straightening rails.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A planing machine with a reversing tool, to plane
both ways.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>jimdandy</ent>⟦br⟧
